text: Taronga Zoo ferry wharf is located on the northern side of Sydney Harbour serving Taronga Zoo. ==Services== Taronga Zoo wharf is served by Sydney Ferries Taronga Zoo services operated by First Fleet and Emerald class ferries. It is also served by Captain Cook Cruises services to Darling Harbour. ==Interchanges== State Transit operates one route to and from Taronga Zoo wharf: *238: to Balmoral Beach ==References== ==External links== *Taronga Zoo Wharf at Transport for New South Wales (Archived 13 June 2019) Category:Ferry wharves in Sydney
title: Taronga Zoo ferry wharf
